@base = http://localhost:4004/orders

### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### SETUP: Create test data
### ═══════════════════════════════════════

### Create a customer
POST {{base}}/Customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Customer",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "city": "Mumbai",
  "creditLimit": 500000
}

### Create an order (use customer ID from above)
POST {{base}}/Orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderNumber": "SO-TEST-001",
  "customer_ID": "b586622f-75ec-46e2-977e-648097ed6e47",
  "orderDate": "2026-06-02",
  "amount": 1500.00,
  "status": "New"
}


### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### BOUND ACTIONS (on specific orders)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════

### Confirm the order
POST {{base}}/Orders(3ed5aae9-38c6-4861-b716-6e792627a5c6)/OrderService.confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Try to confirm again (should fail — already confirmed)
POST {{base}}/Orders(3ed5aae9-38c6-4861-b716-6e792627a5c6)/OrderService.confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Ship the order
POST {{base}}/Orders(3ed5aae9-38c6-4861-b716-6e792627a5c6)/OrderService.ship
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "TRK-2026-001",
  "carrier": "BlueDart"
}

### Deliver the order
POST {{base}}/Orders(3ed5aae9-38c6-4861-b716-6e792627a5c6)/OrderService.deliver
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Try to cancel a delivered order (should fail)
POST {{base}}/Orders(3ed5aae9-38c6-4861-b716-6e792627a5c6)/OrderService.cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Changed my mind"
}
###
GET {{base}}/Orders(3ed5aae9-38c6-4861-b716-6e792627a5c6)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### BOUND FUNCTIONS (read-only, on specific orders)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════

### Get order total (calculated)
GET {{base}}/Orders(3ed5aae9-38c6-4861-b716-6e792627a5c6)/OrderService.getTotal()


### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### UNBOUND ACTIONS (service-level)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════

### Bulk confirm multiple orders
POST {{base}}/bulkConfirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderIds": ["order-uuid-1", "order-uuid-2", "order-uuid-3"]
}


### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### UNBOUND FUNCTIONS (service-level, GET request!)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════

### Get order statistics for June 2026
GET {{base}}/getOrderStats(year=2026,month=6)

### Get top 3 customers by spending
GET {{base}}/getTopCustomers(limit=3)